<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200902/585c0e3cd26143e8811c5b92a36debba.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">▲ 站着喝</span></img></p>
